name: Sunny Side Up
description: Beautiful bright Sunny Side Up inspired this spectrum color, which is made up of a soft crossweave.

name: Dragon Fire
description: Dragon Fire is a rich orange color made up of a tone-on-tone crossweave.

name: Nori
description: Beautiful bright Sunny Side Up inspired this spectrum color, which is made up of a soft crossweave.

name: Catalina
description: Catalina is a tropical blue, bursting with fun. This color is created by a soft crossweave pattern.

name: Candy Apple

name: Gris Deco

name: Nuvo Deco

name: Whitewashed Brick

name: Deco Blanco
description: Deco Blanco is a taupe colored large scale design. The art deco inspired design has a bronze metallic looking pattern over the design.

name: Deco Charcoal
description: Deco Charcoal is an art deco inspired pattern with a metal look in the classic black and gold color combination.

name: Loft Door
description: Loft Door captures the spirit of an old industrial door full of history. This medium scaled design is a very light grey with dark grey and gold scratches throughout the pattern.

name: Big Plaid
description: Big Plaid is a large scale abstracted plaid design. The pattern is monochromatic black and white with a textile texture in the plaid.

name: Classic Marbleized
description: Classic Marbleized is a large scale monochromatic black and white design. The graphic pattern is full of movement from the marbleizing process.

name: Charcoal Tri
description: Charcoal Tri is a small scale abstract design made up of bold multi colored triangles. This monochromatic design can add visual texture and a graphic pop.

name: Dappled Cement
description: Dappled Cement is reminiscent of textured concrete. This large-scale geometric design has various shades of light grey.

name: Dappled Concrete
description: Dappled Concrete is reminiscent of textured concrete. This large-scale geometric design has various shades of grey and charcoal.

name: Swirling Fields
description: Swirling Fields is a large-scale graphic design. This grey on grey pattern is full of organic swirling lines.

name: Calacatta Lincoln
description: Calacatta Lincoln is an extra large-scale white marble with refined warm brown and smoky charcoal directional veining.

name: Mushroom
description: Mushroom is a heathered grey crossweave pattern of rich overall color and detailed interest.

name: Magnolia
description: Magnolia is a white neutral abstract in a soft crossweave pattern offering overall color and extraordinary dimension.

name: Tarnished Kilim
description: Tarnished Kilim is a dark monochromatic steel grey is a modern interpretation of the Kilim rug. This medium scaled allover pattern has a time worn look, adding visual interest.

name: Tide Pool
description: Tide Pool is a soft blue with overlapping patterning that creates a texture.

name: Inky Indigo
description: Inky Indigo is a deep moody blue in an overlapping textural pattern

name: Woven Oak
description: Woven Oak is a warm midtone brown with  organic grid patterns running throughout in a cool grey.

name: Bone Birch
description: Bone Birch is a  midtone warm grey small scale pattern. The pattern come from hand troweled plaster.

name: Detroit Celluloid
description: Detroit Celluloid is a warm tonal copper colored small scale pattern, inspired by old celluloid film clippings.

name: Detroit Film
description: Detroit Film is a small scale pattern in a dimensional tonal  pattern in sepia . The design was inspired from old movie houses and the reels of film.

name: Detroit Black and White
description: Detroit Black and White is a dimensional tone on tone small scale pattern. Reminiscent of old film found on the floor of a movie house in tonal shades of warm grey.

name: Detroit Reel
description: Detroit Reel is inspired by cuttings of old film reels creating a dimensional tonal small scale pattern in cool greys.

name: Linear Chisel Slate
description: Linear Chisel Slate is a deep slate grey marble with a chiseled lineal pattern.

name: Cobalt Shagreen
description: Cobalt Shagreen is a bold stingray pattern that is a small scale all over design in a rich cobalt blue.

name: Striation
description: Striation is an abstracted tonal pattern in a warm white.

name: Linear Chisel Flint
description: Linear Chisel Flint is a medium toned flint grey in a lineal abstract pattern, created by chiseling marble.

name: Linear Chisel Aloe
description: Linear Chisel Aloe is a soft aloe green color. The pattern is made up of a chiseled marble.

name: Linear Chisel Denim
description: Linear Chiseled Denim, is a deep denim blue color, created from chiseled marble.

name: High Rise
description: High Rise is a sophisticated linear abstract in hushed neutrals of beige, grey, and white.

name: Oxidized Silver
description: Oxidized Silver is a time worn charcoal grey metal color made from a crossweave pattern.

name: Game Top Maple
description: Game Top Maple has (4) 35.75” x 35.75” printed game tops.  It has a pre-printed 64 square board in red and black for traditional board games such as chess and checkers and 24 points for backgammon in grey and black on a maple background.

name: Game Top White
description: Game Top White has (4) 35.75” x 35.75” printed game tops.  It has a pre-printed 64 square board in red and black for traditional board games such as chess and checkers and 24 points for backgammon in grey and black on a white background.

name: Know What I Mean
description: Know What I Mean… is a small scale blend of pastel and primary colored jelly beans reminiscent of old time candy jars, visually bursting with flavor.

name: Turf
description: Turf evokes summertime memories of running barefoot through the grass. The lush dark green color and wide blades create pastures and lawns with an overall random pattern that you don’t have to mow.

name: Ice Glass Green
description: Ice Glass Green looks like flowing water that has frozen into a geometric grid. The organic latticework is a small-scale design. The light green, dark green and white colors offer a clarity that can appear translucent.

name: Pictograph Shine (Large)
description: With no apparent beginning or end, this large-scale design is an organized balance of intertwined geometric and curvilinear shapes in green, pink, yellow and tea. The flowing two way pattern reveals a variety of shapes.

name: Baseballs
description: There is no sport that evokes more nostalgia than baseball. This large-scale dense design of Baseballs in traditional white with red stitching is a home run. The multi-directional pattern allows for a wide variety of uses in a sports themed environment.

name: Pictograph Harvest (Large)
description: With no apparent beginning or end, this large-scale design is an organized balance of intertwined geometric and curvilinear shapes in cream, orange, blue and grey. The flowing two way pattern reveals a variety of shapes.

name: Super Highway (Landscape)
description: Super Highway reflects the happy optimism of retro-futurism. This medium-scale design has a grey background of asphalt and futuristic dark grey vehicles. The movement of the cars depicts a frantic pace in an organized pattern.

name: Super Highway
description: Super Highway reflects the happy optimism of retro-futurism. This medium-scale design has a grey background of asphalt and futuristic dark grey vehicles. The movement of the cars depicts a frantic pace in an organized pattern.

name: Big City (Landscape)
description: This large-scale horizontal design is a dense city of sky-scrapers in red-orange, gold, yellow, grey and white. The all-over design of geometric buildings are a unique twist to looking into an urban area and seeing only buildings.

name: Big City Traffic (Landscape)
description: This large scale horizontal mural is a densely built city of skyscrapers in red-orange, gold, yellow, grey and white. Happy commuters make their way past the patterned buildings.

name: Mountain Resort (Landscape)
description: This large-scale design is set against a periwinkle sky, with plump mountains in bright blues, vivid greens and white snowcaps. The linear texture and fluid movement are occasionally interrupted by trees, buildings and billboards.

name: Mountain Resort
description: This large-scale design is set against a periwinkle sky, with plump mountains in bright blues, vivid greens and white snowcaps. The linear texture and fluid movement are occasionally interrupted by trees, buildings and billboards.

name: Cherry Grove
description: Cherry Grove is a large-scale design has rows of pink cotton candy trees, punctuated by smaller feather like trees on a white background. The fine detail of this linear design creates a fun and unique overall grid pattern.

name: Blooming Grove
description: Blooming Grove is a large-scale design has rows of blue lollipop trees, punctuated by stout yellow trees on a white background. The fine detail of this linear design creates a fun and unique overall grid pattern.

name: Luna Night
description: A medium scale abstract. Black and dark grey laminate design come together to create this low contrast monochromatic design.
